import React from "react";
import { Typography, Box, Grid, Paper } from "@mui/material";

function AnalyticsPage() {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ py: 4 }}>
      <Typography variant="h4" component="h1" gutterBottom align="center">
        Dashboard Analitica
      </Typography>
      <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="text.secondary" align="center" sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
        Statistiche dettagliate e andamento dei dati
      </Typography>

      <Grid container spacing={4}>
        {/* Grafico 1 */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Paper elevation={3} sx={{ p: 3 }}>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Grafico Vendite Mensili
            </Typography>
            {/* Qui andrebbe il componente del tuo grafico reale, es. da Recharts */}
            <Box sx={{ height: 200, bgcolor: 'primary.light', display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', alignItems: 'center', color: 'white', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              Grafico Lineare (Placeholder)
            </Box>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
              Andamento delle vendite negli ultimi mesi.
            </Typography>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* Grafico 2 */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Paper elevation={3} sx={{ p: 3 }}>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Distribuzione Utenti
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ height: 200, bgcolor: 'secondary.light', display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', alignItems: 'center', color: 'white', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              Grafico a Torta (Placeholder)
            </Box>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
              Distribuzione demografica degli utenti.
            </Typography>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* Grafico 3 (opzionale) */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Paper elevation={3} sx={{ p: 3 }}>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Report Annuale
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ height: 300, bgcolor: 'info.light', display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', alignItems: 'center', color: 'white', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              Grafico a Barre (Placeholder)
            </Box>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
              Riepilogo delle performance annuali.
            </Typography>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default AnalyticsPage;
